<br>
This can also be a good xp zone for ppl &lt;30, as I believe the last patch boosted XP for dungeons and characters &lt;30. <br>
<br>
I made close to 100pp in 2 hours there one evening with a group of 20-somethings, with everyone splitting loot. I wouldn't feel comfortable soloing here until 30 though, due to the potential for aggro trains.....<br>
<br>
As you get towards 30, you can still make decent plat by killing the guards in the zone. Right now there is no faction penalty for doing so. I got much better xp and pp per hour by killing guards than in mseru, which is supposed to be the better xp zone (I think this may be due to the patch).<br>
<br>
Netherbian Lair is a nice crossing ground for very high level characters, and many will stop and give buffs for people pulling by the main column in center of zone.<br>
<br>
<br>
Naladini Mage of the 29th Season <br>
