<br>
  But considering that 1 Gargoyle eye = 13 pp each and is stackable.. And that golden pendant from there are also worth about 11pp each... it's possible to make goood money....<br>
<br>
  Mobs can also drop some pp's and some FS... and if your lucky you can even get a few goood drops... I know there is a dagger that drops off... a named imp.. I believe....  <br>
<br>
  So if your post 50... then you shouldnt have any problems with the zone... Just make sure not tooo go to deep. Cause.. if you agro 10 green mobs... they can seriously mess you up.... Believe me... <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
